00Z","msg":"拎hardcopy走?<br />\n盤數入哂機,到比人查,乜資料都無咪又係比人入你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45bdef6c1ae3e2c671d602bd5b9ba47c28c21777","tid":1115112,"uid":150347,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:05:31.000Z","msg":"支那係鐘意做埋啲柒事，家陣21世紀，網絡世界，真係唔會天網恢恢疏而不漏？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等睇被踢爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9db44f40c96aa6679b6d3cf6309716e19f12816","tid":1115112,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f7b843f664660d948ed7e548a16756908686d5f","tid":1115112,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"934dff6f9e5a9b3f058a53ca69b5725f79bdc445","tid":1115112,"uid":65328,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:18:08.000Z","msg":"支畜全家做雞既死港支警犬又去咗邊"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:19:54.000Z","msg":"唔見有話報咗警"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T13:13:39.000Z","msg":"刑事罪唔駛查？"},{"pid":"7b2e8320d658feadc45141708c4fe72d1c1471e0","tid":1115112,"uid":20563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T15:09:53.000Z","msg":"之前買機票見到，由香港飛有一段係要同香港航空sharecode, 用香港航空飛機飛<br />\n即刻俾多2000 搭中東三寶買安心<br />\n十月去旅行，一陣佢十月前佢執左我就俾佢玩死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"841a38a06cfce6bd2f364909079fb490aaea7840","tid":1115112,"uid":65328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0f7b843f664660d948ed7e548a16756908686d5f","tid":1115112,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"934dff6f9e5a9b3f058a53ca69b5725f79bdc445","tid":1115112,"uid":65328,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:18:08.000Z","msg":"支畜全家做雞既死港支警犬又去咗邊"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:19:54.000Z","msg":"唔見有話報咗警"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T04:37:00.000Z","msg":"【董事局內鬨　有港航股東報警】<br />\n【指海航強行帶走關鍵財務資料】<br />\n<br />\n發生董事會內閧的香港航空，公司控股股東指責另一個股東海南航空，朝早強行帶走香港航空的關鍵財務資料，已報警處理。<br />\n<br />\n根據香港航空內部員工提供的片段，海航的代表，昨晚已曾意圖在港航辦事處，取走公司關鍵財務資料，結果被阻止。<br />\n<br />\n但港航控股股東鍾國頌指，周四早上海航代表再次進入辦事處，相信有關文件已經被海航銷毀或帶走，具體損失目前難以估量。<br />\n<br />\n不過香港航空發言人回應說，並無任何人闖入公司和帶走資料，指片段中的人士，只是公司外部審計員。<br />\n<br />\n鍾國頌在周二發聲明，指自已重新被委任做香港航空主席，不過代表海航的侯偉，就仍以香港航空主席身份，向員工發出署名電郵，香港航空公司網頁亦無更新。<br />\n<br />\n#有線新聞 #香港航空 #海南航空 #董事局 #內鬨 #財務資料 #報警"},{"pid":"0dd092cc8ab1c3fae0f681fff96c5d2540dfc439","tid":1115112,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5314c45a2cfb571cf291970d49963e6f27bc350f","tid":1115112,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"55d450d05998b9ecbd603e64a68e4bbf47ea79f9","tid":1115112,"uid":106,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T02:56:21.000Z","msg":"屌 買左飛仲未飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:00:49.000Z","msg":"Easter長假先搞呢啲嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T04:37:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}